Package nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.gp21.domain

Interface Tile

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractTile, Acid, Door, Exit, ExitLock, Free, Info, Time, Wall
    public interface Tile
    The tile interface represents a tile in the maze. Some tiles can be moved to by actors and some contains items.
